+- Updated `src/policy/approval_router.py` so `build_policy_preview(...)` always normalizes incoming approval states before delegating to the preview builder.
+- Updated `src/policy/preview.py` so the fallback `preview_unavailable` payload includes `approval_state` and `requires_human_review` in addition to the existing status fields.
+- Updated `tests/test_preview.py` with a regression that covers `preview_enabled=False` plus `manual_review` normalization, and tightened the existing fallback assertions.
+- Updated `docs/approval_policy.md` so the fallback payload example matches the corrected behavior.
+
+## Verification
+
+- `python3 -m unittest tests.test_preview`
+- `python3 -m unittest tests.test_approval_router`
+
+Both test commands passed.
